from a recent and uncalled situation Dracos Awakens to find himself 
about 300 mile out of the reach of any Transformer base. As he runs 
a self diognostic hefinds that allof his parts are working right. 
Dracos then steps out unto the field from underneath a cave like 
structure. and begins to scan around for any recent fights or signs 
of struggle.
